__data__.text:
assistant: 1. Move to the kitchen area.
2. Identify items on top of the wooden cabinet.
3. Pick up each item on the wooden cabinet.
4. Determine the type and function of each item picked up.
5. Return items that are dishes or glasses to the cabinet with a window.
6. Return items that are food or spices to the pantry or relevant storage.
7. Return items that are cooking utensils to the drawer or relevant storage.
8. Move to the countertop.
9. Identify items on the countertop.
10. Pick up each item on the countertop.
11. Determine the type and function of each item picked up.
12. Return items that are dishes or glasses to the cabinet with a window.
13. Return items that are food or spices to the pantry or relevant storage.
14. Return items that are cooking utensils to the drawer or relevant storage.
15. Move to the sink area.
16. Identify items on the drainboard.
17. Pick up each item on the drainboard.
18. Determine the type and function of each item picked up.
19. Return items that are dishes or glasses to the cabinet with a window.
20. Return items that are food or spices to the pantry or relevant storage.
21. Return items that are cooking utensils to the drawer or relevant storage.
22. Move to the refrigerator.
23. Identify items on the shelves of the refrigerator.
24. Pick up each item that is not in its standard storage location.
25. Determine the type and function of each item picked up.
26. Return items that are food or drinks to their standard storage locations.
27. Move to the dining room area.
28. Identify items on the table.
29. Pick up each item on the table.
30. Determine the type and function of each item picked up.
31. Return items that are dishes or glasses to the cabinet with a window.
32. Return items that are food or spices to the pantry or relevant storage.
33. Return items that are cooking utensils to the drawer or relevant storage.
34. Return food packaging to the trash or recycling.
35. Verify all items are in their standard storage locations.
36. Confirm the kitchen is in an organized state.
